Email:		
&&
Please state your full email address, i.e. not only your user name but
also the full domain and site information. 

E.g. edchakom@cd.chalmers.se
##
s
&&
Reference:	
&&
Please state a reference (if you have any) to an established player on
this mud who knows you and can recommend you. Give player name and
email address.

E.g. Zaphod:edchakom@cd.chalmers.se
##
s
&&
Player name:	
&&
Please state the name you would like your mud character to have if we
choose to accept your application. If possible, give several alternatives
since the name you choose might already be taken.

E.g. Zaphod, Beeblebrox
##
m
&&
Comment:	
&&
If you have any comment to this application, something we ought to
know that's not covered by the above questions, please write that
here. Terminate the commentary by entering two asterisks (**) on an
empty line and pressing return.
